Text: Thank you! You are correct that it's not the worst it's like getting a shot. Terrible in theory not too bad in practice.

Author: jazminonacloud
Text: Hey, at least sushi isn’t the worst thing you can binge on. I know it’s hard but try to enjoy the time with your dad and make some memories ❤️  Side note, sashimi is a good option and fairly low-cal, along with miso soup and cucumber rolls.
